                        <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/3840: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-05-27T15:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">May 27,
                                        1922—3 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>132. Department approves your taking the position indicated in your
                            telegram No. 232 [<hi rend="italic">233</hi>], May 26, noon.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
